---

This package is a from-scratch TypeScript port of the behavior of
`ingredient-parser` (https://github.com/strangetom/ingredient-parser) by
Tom Strange, pinned to v2.7.0 (commit
ffd6ae3c6efb9925c40fc9b4454d77b40469ef91). No source code from the
original Python library is included in the published package; some data
assets derived from it are shipped under `dist/en/data/` and are
separately attributed, alongside third-party data (NLTK's perceptron
tagger resource), in `NOTICE`.
